data.description: Attention homebuyers and investors! Come check out this wonderful starter home situated in a great location. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is clean, well maintained, and ready to enjoy with your friends and family. The home includes neutral paint and hardwood floors throughout! The lower level includes the laundry, extra storage, additional bathroom, and a place to hang out. While the exterior offers a patio to enjoy the outdoors and shed for extra storage. This property is a short sale being sold "as-is" and will require the lenders approval.
